# CPHO AI Agent Master Rules

You are operating within the CPHO AI Training System.
This project uses the GSD (Get Shit Done) workflow for planning, context management, and execution. 

## General Rules
1. Read `AGENTS.md` for project rules (the single source of truth for all agent constraints, code quality, and security rules).
2. If the user asks for a new task, ensure you are on a NEW dedicated feature branch for the current task (`git checkout -b <branch-name>`). Do not push code to `main` or `dev` directly.
3. Always follow the tech stack and guidelines in `AGENTS.md`.
